  "sentences": [
    {
      "id": "u10-s1",
      "text": "Imagine staying on an island alone.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-p1",
      "keywords": [
        "imagine",
        "island",
        "alone"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-s2",
      "text": "You can only take five things with you.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-p1",
      "keywords": [
        "take",
        "five",
        "things"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-s3",
      "text": "You might put food, water, tools and clothes on your list.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-p1",
      "keywords": [
        "put",
        "food",
        "water",
        "tools",
        "clothes",
        "list"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-s4",
      "text": "But what about the fifth one?",
      "paragraphId": "u10-p1",
      "keywords": [
        "fifth",
        "one"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-s5",
      "text": "Most people would choose something for fun, like a novel, a magazine or a solar media player.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-p2",
      "keywords": [
        "choose",
        "fun",
        "novel",
        "magazine",
        "solar media player"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-s6",
      "text": "After all, no one wants to get bored!",
      "paragraphId": "u10-p2",
      "keywords": [
        "after all",
        "no one",
        "get bored"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-s7",
      "text": "Fun can do away with bad feelings and lift our spirits.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-p2",
      "keywords": [
        "do away with",
        "bad feelings",
        "lift",
        "spirits"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-s8",
      "text": "Just picture yourself watching a funny film on that island.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-p3",
      "keywords": [
        "picture",
        "watching",
        "funny film",
        "island"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-s9",
      "text": "Sitting under the trees will not be boring at all.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-p4",
      "keywords": [
        "sitting",
        "trees",
        "boring"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-s10",
      "text": "It becomes a moment of joy.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-p4",
      "keywords": [
        "becomes",
        "moment",
        "joy"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-s11",
      "text": "Fun also keeps us feeling youthful.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-p5",
      "keywords": [
        "keeps",
        "feeling",
        "youthful"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-s12",
      "text": "As George Bernard Shaw once said, \"We don't stop playing because we grow old; we grow old because we stop playing.\"",
      "paragraphId": "u10-p5",
      "keywords": [
        "George Bernard Shaw",
        "stop playing",
        "grow old"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-s13",
      "text": "Research also shows that fun brings people closer.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-p5",
      "keywords": [
        "research",
        "shows",
        "brings",
        "closer"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-s14",
      "text": "No one is an island.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-p5",
      "keywords": [
        "no one",
        "island"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-s15",
      "text": "Having fun is a good way to connect with others.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-p5",
      "keywords": [
        "good way",
        "connect",
        "others"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-s16",
      "text": "So, next time, invite your friends to enjoy live music together.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-p5",
      "keywords": [
        "invite",
        "friends",
        "enjoy",
        "live music"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-s17",
      "text": "It's not just about having fun - you will be closer because of the shared experience!",
      "paragraphId": "u10-p5",
      "keywords": [
        "shared experience",
        "closer"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-s18",
      "text": "Fun is important in a number of ways.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-p5",
      "keywords": [
        "important",
        "number of ways"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-s19",
      "text": "Don't forget to take some time out to have fun and enjoy life!",
      "paragraphId": "u10-p5",
      "keywords": [
        "take time out",
        "enjoy life"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-s20",
      "text": "We need to work hard.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-p5",
      "keywords": [
        "work hard"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "u10-s21",
      "text": "But we should be able to play hard, too.",
      "paragraphId": "u10-p5",
      "keywords": [
        "play hard"
      ]
    }
  ],
